The new post of High Representative for Foreign Affairs and Defence Policy was explained by the Commissioner in her answer to the question: 'Who is who in the European Union?' 'Which telephone number should I call?' as an important step towards uniformity and greater clarity of the Union's policy towards states such as China or India.
Nobody wants to ban us from our syrecky.
Mrs Vicenova also referred to the agenda that the European Council has lived, lives and will live in the near future.
She described the Czech presidency two years ago as a success.
The Czechs have solved the financial crisis, the gas crisis or organised a summit for the Eastern Partnership.
She described the fall of the government as very negative and damaged the image of the Czech Republic.
The Czech representation to the EU is very busy at the moment.
